item.description:
Meet up with other area developers for some tech chat and coffee.

We have another meeting coming up, Thursday. We'll be
meeting up at our usual haunt, Panera Bread in Hadley and we'll be
gathering towards the back of the restaurant. Come join us for some
coffee, a snack, and some pleasant chatting about all things
development.

We meet up twice every month (every other Thursday).


scroll to bottom of page and look to the right:
http://wmassdevs.com/....
